metadata.name: Evil Plot #1: Poison The Food Supply
metadata.description: Cartoonist and Mastermind Jordan Lyric has gathered the very best and healthiest Foods of the NFT Community with one goal in mind ⁠— to CORRUPT them, POISONING them one by one. Unleashing upon the blockchain an army of EVIL FOODS ⁠— devilish little minions to do our horrible bidding! This limited edition artwork commemorates a TERRIFYING community event, and Jordan Lyric's own descent into diabolical madness!
